<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>$pageTitle</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="$req.contextPath/download/resources/com.projmodel.projmodel:projmodel-resources/projmodel.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="projmodel-container">
    <div class="projmodel-header">
        <a href="$req.contextPath/plugins/servlet/projmodel" class="projmodel-back-link">← На главную</a>
        <h1>$pageTitle</h1>
        <p class="projmodel-subtitle">$pageDescription</p>
        <p class="projmodel-version">Version: 1.0.0-demo</p>
    </div>

    <div class="projmodel-card" style="text-align: center; padding: 60px 20px;">
        <div class="projmodel-mvp-badge">
            $status
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; margin: 30px 0; color: #5e6c84;">
            $statusMessage
        </p>
        <div class="projmodel-mock-list">
            <div class="mock-item">
                <span class="mock-name">А</span>
                <div class="mock-progress"><div class="mock-progress-bar" style="width: 45%;">45%</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="mock-item">
                <span class="mock-name">Ар</span>
                <div class="mock-progress"><div class="mock-progress-bar" style="width: 82%;">82%</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="mock-item">
                <span class="mock-name">И</span>
                <div class="mock-progress"><div class="mock-progress-bar" style="width: 63%;">63%</div></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: #7a869a;">
            В финальной версии: реальные данные из Jira, цветовая индикация перегрузки, рекомендации
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="projmodel-footer">
        ProjModel — умный помощник для Jira
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>